  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nThat method returns only once its scheduler has run out of requests to make, but we need a way to tell it to stop anyway (e.g. when we get a SIGINT)\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\nAdd something like `LightChain._should_stop`, to `StateDownloader`, and have `run()` exit when it is set. \r\n\r\nIf we fix #280 first, this should be really straightforward\r\n",
